reviewText: Bought the whole series from AMZ  LOVE IT.
Dont like how each disk only holds two episodes. This was obviously made by hand and recorded.
Had seen True Blood on HBO and wanted to watch all seasons again!  Love it!  The writing and acting is super!!  Recommend it highly!
First season is PERFECT!!! After that.. It's ok
It was a gift for my mother in law and she loved it!
A GREAT SERIES AND GREAT QUALITY
